Class FDSNWebServicesRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • gov.usgs.anss.fetcher.Fetcher
        • gov.usgs.anss.fetcher.FDSNWebServicesRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public final class FDSNWebServicesRequest
extends Fetcher
    This class gets a segment of time series from a FDSN waveserver for the Fetcher. It makes up a FDSNWebService command line for the FDSN CWBFetchData script and executes it, waits for completion, and processes any returned file.
